# {{ .Name }} frontend

Requires Node LTS and pnpm. The API should listen on `http://localhost:8080`.

```sh
pnpm install
pnpm api:generate
pnpm dev
```

Run `pnpm test`, `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm build`, and `pnpm test:e2e` for verification. TanStack Query owns server state; Zustand is reserved for client-only UI state. Never edit `src/shared/api/generated` manually.
